{"tid":326782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 云伯向熱狗開火！","createTime":"2017-07-18T09:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T12:32:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc5e2b46c54843c5d363d15c00105b68a1bccdd","tid":326782,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"Sze Tat Chau<br />\n5 小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n陳云根「清算」鄭松泰了。面臨DQ案的鄭松泰議員，早前還聲嘶力竭為陳云根、熱狗發動之「清算」保駕護航，宣稱有「公共性」 ，甚至「清算」到毓民頭上，也不懸崖勒馬，反而變本加厲。現在其議員資格朝不保夕，陳云根隨即展開「清算」；一旦遭到DQ，陳云根必打落水狗。熱狗出賣毓民，轉投陳云根，看來很快自食惡果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20139633_10155285015717254_3692642833015963484_n.jpg?oh=a93764dd48388bc0d51a5b79785583ae&amp;oe=59FAEB4B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20139633_10155285015717254_3692642833015963484_n.jpg%3Foh%3Da93764dd48388bc0d51a5b79785583ae%26oe%3D59FAEB4B&h=11ffba83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7208791931ae384e6b7e48c8d061266999b75ad8","tid":326782,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:16:43.000Z","msg":"CLS！<br />\n<br />\n連蟲泰同邊個企都要佢管！<br />\n<br />\n邪教黎！"},{"pid":"06bf83f7dcac5e6dca767ed84521c22b028af2a7","tid":326782,"uid":28435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CLS！<br />\n<br />\n連蟲泰同邊個企都要佢管！<br />\n<br />\n邪教黎！</blockquote><br />\n咁泰囝做得黃洋達隻狗就預左啦"},{"pid":"b46d337185cca0c3556aba8ea88a05f035dc394a","tid":326782,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CLS！<br />\n<br />\n連蟲泰同邊個企都要佢管！<br />\n<br />\n邪教黎！</blockquote><br />\n咁泰囝做得黃洋達隻狗就預左啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一直都係做下靶<br />\n<br />\n仲話乜野博士 (北大), 做狗一樣"},{"pid":"c049d71a40c692f48b91cfa2669e67d6dbad2402","tid":326782,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":